# Cursor Rules for Digital Metrics API

## File Organization

- src/: Core application code
- services/: External service integrations
- tests/: Test files
- docs/: Documentation
- config/: Configuration files

## Coding Standards

- Follow PEP 8
- Use type hints
- Document all functions and classes
- Comprehensive error handling

## Testing Requirements

- Unit tests for all components
- Integration tests for services
- Test coverage requirements

## Documentation

- Update Memory Bank for all changes
- Document architectural decisions
- Maintain API documentation

## Task Integration

- Automatically integrate task breakdowns from docs/tasks/ into memory-bank/tasks.md
- Follow the rules in .cursor/rules/003-task_integration.mdc
